        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer10363429" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17037134744090385217">Seriously, Laurell K. Hamilton used to write good vampire-slayer novels. Now she writes erotica. Don&apos;t get me wrong, I like erotica as much as the next guy (or gal), but when I want to read a vampire slayer novel, I want to read a vampire slayer novel!!! Damn you, Anita Blake.</span>
  <span id="freeText17037134744090385217" style="display:none">Seriously, Laurell K. Hamilton used to write good vampire-slayer novels. Now she writes erotica. Don't get me wrong, I like erotica as much as the next guy (or gal), but when I want to read a vampire slayer novel, I want to read a vampire slayer novel!!! Damn you, Anita Blake.</span>
